divs: Sighting Detailson my way home, notice several brights lights and unusual object in air over trees. slowed down to observe, didn't know what it was. I was stunned couldn't believe what I was seeing. It was about nine objects going straight up in the air. went home got husband took him to sight he witness same unusual objects. we were both in shock trying to figure out what we had witness. we stayed there and watch the objects until they disappeared going up in the sky.
